Boot with Live CD


Open a terminal ......


1. sudo mkdir /mnt/myroot

2. sudo mount /dev/[partition with /boot i.e. sda1] → /mnt/myroot

3. sudo mount --bind /dev  /mnt/myroot/dev

4. sudo mount --bind /sys  /mnt/myroot/sys

5. sudo mount --bind /proc  /mnt/myroot/proc

6. sudo chroot /mnt/myroot → will change prompt

7. sudo grub-install /dev/[partition i.e. sda not sda1]

8. reboot 
